# Wiki pages

Template: `wiki/_page-template.md`. Policy: [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) (Wiki value-add policy).

**Do not** create pages that only link to `/raw`, contain truncated excerpts, or leave internal/kernel links unprocessed.

**Do** read full sources (and linked pages where needed), extract guidance, and write synthesized Summary / Key Information / Practical Guidance with source citations.

## Required sections

`# Title` → `## Summary` → `## Key Information` → `## Practical Guidance` → `## Related Concepts` → `## Related Organisations` → `## Sources`

## Category directories

| Directory | Use for |
|-----------|---------|
| `wiki/topics/` | Broad subject areas |
| `wiki/concepts/` | Rights, obligations, definitions |
| `wiki/procedures/` | Processes, applications, deadlines |
| `wiki/organisations/` | Advisers, courts, regulators |
| `wiki/funding/` | Legal aid, pro bono, fees |
| `wiki/courts/` | Courts, tribunals, hearings |
| `wiki/regulations/` | CPR, practice directions, statutes |

## Sources section format

```markdown
- **Citizens Advice** — [Budgeting](https://...) — `raw/citizens-advice/debt-and-money-budgeting.md`
```

Link to the raw file path and original URL from the source frontmatter.

## After changes

Update category `_index.md`, `wiki/index.md`, and `logs/ingestion-log.md`.
